{"tid":1490530,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"極端主義幾時出現？","createTime":"2019-08-20T06:40:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T09:36:02.000Z","uid":4379,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fe0fc68c0156d204b4d87d6299fe974b7a45fecc","tid":1490530,"uid":4379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:40:26.000Z","msg":"成日聽到唔知咩爽話極端主義已經喺香港出現，歷史亦同我講香港依個情況係一撚定會有地下組織出現<br />\n<br />\n點解到今時今日我哋都淨係喺得連登話要咩打撚斷佢班唔知咩生物(唔想侮辱真狗)嘅手同腳，點解仲未有<br />\n<br />\n早幾日我仲覺得818依場做俾外國睇嘅show好撚成功，但係今日起身睇到啲片，我唔知講咩好，係嬲撚到唔知講咩好<br />\n<br />\n我自己好細膽，同前線手足比我同狗無分別，但係依一刻我真係好希望有極端主義嘅出現，法律已經制裁唔到佢哋嘅時候，點解我哋仲要忍，點解仲要理咩民意同道德？<br />\n<br />\n對唔住，依一刻我嬲撚到唔知可以做咩，已經唔知自己打撚左篇垃圾出嚟，但係我只係想講，就算手足真係玩極端主義，我都一撚定唔割"},{"pid":"02daf8e329f0ffd263678654b0c140c8d6822852","tid":1490530,"uid":4379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:42:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bd0c0af829e4f0ff3e69fce470e3ae186424a954","tid":1490530,"uid":4379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:44:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89bac2fa5030c56037383e39c1412447bbd29a5e","tid":1490530,"uid":4379,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:44:50.000Z","msg":"求下大家，咪撚再理咩民意同道德"},{"pid":"176f56135fcb83671e1c88550131495108d490db","tid":1490530,"uid":4379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:46:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a88482b91216e37abc0155832af382f18c3c40b7","tid":1490530,"uid":4379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:46:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b6b6ec10218e1f06c92199ce5703db27b0bb7ed4","tid":1490530,"uid":4379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:47:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2030070e48237b54b4afe50dffb8be2f00b84ff7","tid":1490530,"uid":4379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:48:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bc3f1e77698c7ce5519843f2f82e17b2912239e5","tid":1490530,"uid":4379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:50:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7bee6c4ac17cf8aef9e566a6f291642831729dc6","tid":1490530,"uid":4379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:51:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2c0ac63e8b1c553da3f713779d9eab1dc6bf5c60","tid":1490530,"uid":4379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:51:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7221db191cc4a691aaed2e309a9c7954c984b6ef","tid":1490530,"uid":4379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:54:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"58b5d5f0c8c9075296e09b39bdd0f3eba4f8d630","tid":1490530,"uid":4379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:58:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cb2add6b5d88efed625736fad9dba4d306f2b6f4","tid":1490530,"uid":125680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:35:05.000Z","msg":"已經出現左兩個極端主義：<br />\nChinazi &amp; hkfascism<br />\n<br />\n係度迫害香港人與全球追求自由公義的人"},{"pid":"57629b42d38307ff26d3cad1dfdb910505cd1eff","tid":1490530,"uid":4379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb2add6b5d88efed625736fad9dba4d306f2b6f4","tid":1490530,"uid":125680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:35:05.000Z","msg":"已經出現左兩個極端主義：<br />\nChinazi &amp; hkfascism<br />\n<br />\n係度迫害香港人與全球追求自由公義的人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:36:02.000Z","msg":"我哋幾時迫害返佢哋....<br />\n<br />\n禍必及妻兒"}]}